1
00:00:00,710 --> 00:00:03,610
(Episode 122)

2
00:00:05,440 --> 00:00:08,550
Who drew this one?
Did you draw this one too, Bo Ra?

3
00:00:08,710 --> 00:00:12,980
Yes. My grandma is really good
at making four-leaf clover bracelets.

4
00:00:13,150 --> 00:00:15,720
And she's great
at embroidering handkerchiefs.

5
00:00:16,050 --> 00:00:19,590
I saw her embroidery,
and then I drew this.

6
00:00:20,730 --> 00:00:23,560
- Your grandma?
- Yes, her name is Jung Suk Hee.

7
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:27,170
You don't even know my grandma's name,
Grandfather?

8
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:29,630
I suppose I don't.

9
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:48,620
Seong Sil was good
at making four-leaf clovers too.

10
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:51,220
How could Jung Suk Hee...

11
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:57,660
What if Chairman Ma gets suspicious
about the necklace?

12
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:02,430
Why did Jung Suk Hee wear the necklace
and cause me all this trouble?

13
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:05,900
She's been useless my whole life.
She's always getting in my way.

14
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,970
This won't do.

15
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:12,110
I can't just be sitting around here
while Jung Suk Hee's at the house.

16
00:01:12,780 --> 00:01:14,610
I have to kick her out
of the house somehow.

17
00:01:14,610 --> 00:01:15,650
This is making me too anxious.

18
00:01:22,050 --> 00:01:23,050
Have a seat.

19
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:31,260
Jun Ho.

20
00:01:31,930 --> 00:01:34,930
- How did you get this?
- This...

21
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:36,900
belongs to Baek Ho.

22
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,870
Kang Baek Ho? You mean the lawyer?

23
00:01:40,770 --> 00:01:44,080
Yes. Apparently, it's what he had with him
when he came to the infant home.

24
00:01:45,010 --> 00:01:46,610
Kang Baek Ho was at the infant home?

25
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:51,880
Manager Lee, come over here.

26
00:01:55,650 --> 00:01:58,720
- This is...
- He says this belongs to Kang Baek Ho.

27
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:01,460
Do you know anything about
how this happened?

28
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:02,790
Manager Lee.

29
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:04,930
If you know anything,
please tell us what's going on.

30
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,870
How would I know anything?

31
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:11,340
- What I told you before is all there is.
- Is that so?

32
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:14,340
Where is the infant home
that Kang Baek Ho...

33
00:02:14,770 --> 00:02:15,810
was adopted from?

34
00:02:16,510 --> 00:02:19,640
No, on second thought,
I'll go to the infant home myself...

35
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:22,510
and find out why Kang Baek Ho has this.

36
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:25,880
Why on earth he has this golden toad.

37
00:02:26,990 --> 00:02:29,950
- No, wait, ma'am.
- Let go of me.

38
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:31,690
You know something, don't you?

39
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:35,160
You can't fool me.
What is it? Spit it out.

40
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:37,900
Tell me the secret you've been hiding.

41
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:39,630
She's right, Manager Lee.

42
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,870
If you know something, please tell us.

43
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:47,840
Is Kang Baek Ho CEO Chae's son?

44
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,840
Tell us.

45
00:02:53,410 --> 00:02:55,410
No, that's ridiculous.

46
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:58,650
Lee Kang Hyuk, hurry up and tell me.
Tell me the truth.

47
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:02,150
There's no way Kang Baek Ho is my son.
Spit it out.

48
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,060
I'm sorry.

49
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:14,200
You mean...

50
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,330
Kang Baek Ho is my son?

51
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:25,340
The building burned to the ground,
so the original registry was closed,

52
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,840
only the land ledger remains.

53
00:03:27,510 --> 00:03:30,250
This huge piece of prime real estate.

54
00:03:30,950 --> 00:03:32,080
If I can follow the money,

55
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:34,250
I should be able to tell
if a crime was committed.

56
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,830
Mom!

57
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,760
What is it?

58
00:03:46,730 --> 00:03:47,900
My golden toad is missing.

59
00:03:48,330 --> 00:03:50,840
- Did anyone go into my room?
- What do you mean it's missing?

60
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:54,740
I think I saw
Jun Ho go into your room earlier.

61
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:55,870
Jun Ho did?

62
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:57,940
Is it really true?

63
00:04:00,210 --> 00:04:02,010
Is Kang Baek Ho really CEO Chae's son?

64
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:06,450
- That's impossible.
- How could this happen, Lee Kang Hyuk?

65
00:04:07,350 --> 00:04:10,390
How can Kang Baek Ho possibly be my son?

66
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:12,190
I only ever gave birth to Jun Ho.

67
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:14,830
Who else did I supposedly give birth to?
Does this make any sense?

68
00:04:15,090 --> 00:04:18,330
How can I have another son
that I never even gave birth to?

69
00:04:20,030 --> 00:04:22,230
General Manager Kang,
could you please give us a moment?

70
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:32,810
Calm down.

71
00:04:34,010 --> 00:04:35,950
Back then, 30 years ago,

72
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:39,680
you were pregnant with Ma Dong Seok's son,
remember?

73
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,520
I'm afraid...

74
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:44,260
the baby had already passed away.

75
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:47,130
Bring him back.

76
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:48,930
I said, bring him back!

77
00:04:50,030 --> 00:04:51,700
But that baby died.

78
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,900
The doctor pronounced him dead,

79
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:57,400
but he started breathing again
right after.

80
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,910
- What?
- But his breathing was faint,

81
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:05,040
and it was touch and go,
he could stop breathing at any moment.

82
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:07,650
So I thought it would be better
to just say he was dead.

83
00:05:07,650 --> 00:05:09,180
That's why I didn't tell you.

84
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,450
I didn't want you to get your hopes up...

85
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,650
only to be hurt all over again.

86
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:16,490
So?

87
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:19,160
Luckily, his breathing returned to normal,

88
00:05:20,790 --> 00:05:23,730
so I secretly took him to the infant home.

89
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:25,800
So that baby is Kang Baek Ho?

90
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,270
Is my son really Kang Baek Ho?

91
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:32,500
The son I had with Ma Dong Seok
is Kang Baek Ho?

92
00:05:32,570 --> 00:05:33,570
No.

93
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,570
I went to the infant home and checked.

94
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:38,080
When I left him
in front of the infant home,

95
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:40,680
I tucked a golden toad in with him.

96
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,410
But I went back to the infant home
recently to check,

97
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:46,450
and they told me he didn't live long
and died of pneumonia.

98
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:50,290
You bastard.

99
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:54,860
How could you take my son
and hide him from me without a word?

100
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:59,300
How could you lie to me that he was dead?

101
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:03,870
Hwa Young, you belong to me.

102
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:06,240
But you had another man's child?

103
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:07,970
That child...

104
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:13,110
- was meant to die from the start.
- That's insane.

105
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,480
If you hadn't taken him away,

106
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:20,620
- he would have lived!
- No!

107
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:23,790
He still would have died.

108
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,890
You nearly miscarried.
He didn't even cry at birth, remember?

109
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:30,530
Is that supposed to be your excuse?

110
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,400
If you hadn't taken my baby,

111
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:36,470
I never would have stolen...

112
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,940
Jung Suk Hee's daughter,

113
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:43,270
and I wouldn't have all this blood
on my hands.

114
00:06:43,670 --> 00:06:46,940
You're the one behind all of my crimes.
It was all you.

115
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:49,980
Hwa Young.

116
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:54,220
Have you ever once stopped
to think about me?

117
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:57,260
Even after you gave birth
to our son, Jun Ho,

118
00:06:59,090 --> 00:07:01,560
you still weren't happy and had a child
with that bastard Ma Dong Seok?

119
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:05,900
What man would be okay
with watching that happen?

120
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:09,130
Watching your belly grow
bigger and bigger...

121
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:13,200
made me so furious
I could hardly stand it.

122
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:15,870
The one to blame for all of this isn't me.

123
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:18,880
It's you, Chae Hwa Young, and your greed!

124
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:21,180
Shut up.

125
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:26,920
Say that again.

126
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:29,150
What did you just say?

127
00:07:31,490 --> 00:07:33,360
That you, Lee Kang Hyuk, are my father?

128
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:37,830
- Jun Ho.
- No, that's not true, Jun Ho.

129
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:40,030
There's no way Lee Kang Hyuk
could be your father.

130
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:43,000
Your father is a much better
and more decent man.

131
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:45,070
Not some criminal like Lee Kang Hyuk,

132
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:48,240
who has blood on his hands
and does all kinds of dirty work.

133
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:49,310
Chae Hwa Young.

134
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,910
Are you going to keep this up?

135
00:07:52,610 --> 00:07:54,050
It's time to tell the truth.

136
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,750
Please.

137
00:07:56,110 --> 00:08:00,120
- Stop denying who his father is, please!
- That's enough!

138
00:08:02,650 --> 00:08:03,650
Stop it, both of you.

139
00:08:13,930 --> 00:08:16,170
You should have kept your mouth shut
until the very end.

140
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:18,740
You call yourself a father
after hurting Jun Ho like that?

141
00:08:19,340 --> 00:08:20,640
So what are you going to do now?

142
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:24,980
What about Jun Ho? What will you do?
Tell me! What are you going to do?

143
00:08:32,450 --> 00:08:33,920
Even after you gave birth
to our son, Jun Ho...

144
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:35,620
There's no way Lee Kang Hyuk
could be your father.

145
00:08:35,690 --> 00:08:37,050
Not some criminal like Lee Kang Hyuk,

146
00:08:37,050 --> 00:08:38,390
who has blood on his hands
and does all kinds of dirty work.

147
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:42,260
Stop denying who his father is, please!

148
00:08:43,590 --> 00:08:45,230
Lee Kang Hyuk is my father?

149
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:47,200
I'll never accept it.

150
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,970
No. It can't be.

151
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:51,170
Absolutely not!

152
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,640
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

153
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,040
Jang Mi.

154
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:04,480
So you managed to take some
of CEO Chae's slush fund?

155
00:09:04,950 --> 00:09:07,950
Yes. I faked an investment
in Hills Hotel...

156
00:09:07,950 --> 00:09:09,820
and collected
a 30 million dollar penalty fee.

157
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:15,460
I think you're ready to take over
Dream Group, Jang Mi.

158
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:19,060
But the problem is...

159
00:09:19,330 --> 00:09:22,500
we don't know the full extent
of CEO Chae's slush fund.

160
00:09:23,170 --> 00:09:27,100
I know she's been getting kickbacks
from our hotel's subcontractors,

161
00:09:27,310 --> 00:09:30,440
and she's likely funneled a lot of money
through shell companies.

162
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:32,980
It won't be easy,

163
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,880
but we must investigate discreetly...

164
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,250
and have her arrested for embezzlement
as soon as possible.

165
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:39,350
I'll handle it with Lawyer Kang Baek Ho.

166
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,690
- Please let us do this, Grandfather.
- You've done well.

167
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:44,920
That's enough for now, Jang Mi.

168
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:48,390
- What?
- You've always asked me, haven't you?

169
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:52,400
Why I still keep CEO Chae around.

170
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:53,930
You think...

171
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:57,700
I had no idea she had a slush fund
all this time?

172
00:09:58,370 --> 00:10:00,440
It's all Dream Group's money, after all.

173
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:04,340
My plan was to bleed her dry,

174
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:07,980
collect every last penny,

175
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,350
- and kick her out.
- But Grandfather,

176
00:10:11,780 --> 00:10:13,520
CEO Chae has committed too many crimes.

177
00:10:13,850 --> 00:10:15,790
We should have her arrested
for embezzlement first,

178
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,890
- then pile on the other charges...
- That's too big of a risk.

179
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:22,960
If we jail her rashly
and she hides the money away,

180
00:10:23,490 --> 00:10:24,860
we'll never find it again.

181
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,370
You can make her pay
for her crimes anytime,

182
00:10:28,770 --> 00:10:31,240
but once money is hidden,
it's gone for good.

183
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:35,970
So let me handle big things like this.

184
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:38,640
You just focus on the job you were given.

185
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,280
Understand?

186
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,510
Yes, Grandfather.

187
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,920
This room is so nice.

188
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:06,700
This is my grandma's!

189
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,540
Grandma!

190
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:14,950
- Grandma!
- Bo Ra, don't run. You'll hurt yourself.

191
00:11:15,410 --> 00:11:17,150
Grandma, this is yours.

192
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,760
This is a present for Grandpa.

193
00:11:26,090 --> 00:11:28,760
I'll give this to him on our picnic.

194
00:11:29,130 --> 00:11:31,830
I'll give this to Grandpa for you, Mom.

195
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:38,340
This is my four-leaf clover bracelet.

196
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:43,340
I found it in that other grandma's room.

197
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:47,550
Look at this little brat.

198
00:11:48,250 --> 00:11:50,580
How dare you go into someone's room
and steal their things?

199
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:52,480
Give it here.

200
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,690
Chae Hwa Young, you're the thief.

201
00:11:54,690 --> 00:11:57,320
Bo Ra was returning Suk Hee's bracelet.

202
00:11:57,390 --> 00:12:01,560
How dare you accuse an innocent person?
Have you stooped to using a kid to steal?

203
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:04,260
- Give it here!
- No!

204
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:06,100
No!

205
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,440
Father, look.

206
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:25,450
Jung Suk Hee keeps sneaking into my room
and stealing my things!

207
00:12:25,650 --> 00:12:29,050
And she's now insisting
that a bracelet I cherish is hers!

208
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:31,920
That bracelet is my mother's.

209
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:34,360
Have you really stooped
to stealing my mother's things now?

210
00:12:34,430 --> 00:12:35,430
Shut up.

211
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:37,560
This mother-daughter duo
is ganging up to frame me.

212
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:38,960
Why would I steal it?

213
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:42,630
That's ridiculous.
Seo Rin gave this to me.

214
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:45,670
I think we all know
who's being ridiculous here.

215
00:12:46,740 --> 00:12:49,910
Father, I can't live like this.
I'm constantly on edge.

216
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,640
Please keep Oh Jang Mi and her family
out of my room.

217
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:55,580
Chae Hwa Young, you're the bad thief
who stole what's not yours.

218
00:12:55,850 --> 00:12:59,050
Father, you're not believing this halfwit,
are you?

219
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:02,520
- "A halfwit?" Watch your mouth.
- That's enough!

220
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,290
Quiet!

221
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,500
Sir, you sent for me?

222
00:13:21,410 --> 00:13:24,610
Do a thorough background check
on Jung Suk Hee.

223
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:29,310
Pardon? You mean Oh Jang Mi's mother?

224
00:13:29,650 --> 00:13:30,810
Why the sudden interest?

225
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:35,390
That viper, Chae Hwa Young,
is stealing things from Jung Suk Hee.

226
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:39,520
The four-leaf clover
that Seong Sil always cherished,

227
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:42,060
and even the matching necklace we shared.

228
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:44,160
Now, why would she be trying
to steal them?

229
00:13:45,430 --> 00:13:49,130
Both of those items are connected
to my daughter, Eun Hye.

230
00:13:49,330 --> 00:13:51,670
But even setting aside
the DNA test results,

231
00:13:52,070 --> 00:13:54,470
the AI composite sketch
also pointed to CEO Chae.

232
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:56,840
That composite sketch and the DNA test...

233
00:13:57,240 --> 00:14:01,010
If Chae Hwa Young puts her mind to it,
you think she can't fake a piece of paper?

234
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:08,250
Hey! You can't just park like that!

235
00:14:08,590 --> 00:14:09,820
- Please call me later.
- Forget it.

236
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:11,990
- Let's go to the police station.
- Okay, fine. Let go so we can talk.

237
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:13,090
You think you're the only one in a rush?

238
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:15,330
I'm busy too. Let's go.

239
00:14:17,190 --> 00:14:20,460
Seong Hye said that Jung Suk Hee...

240
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,830
looks just like my wife.

241
00:14:25,270 --> 00:14:27,500
That necklace Chae Hwa Young has...

242
00:14:28,310 --> 00:14:30,740
belongs to Eun Hye.

243
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:34,310
And yet, when Chae Hwa Young
saw a similar one,

244
00:14:34,450 --> 00:14:38,320
she claimed it was hers
and took it away from Jung Suk Hee.

245
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:41,350
And today,
with that four-leaf clover bracelet,

246
00:14:41,490 --> 00:14:44,020
she proved once again that she's a fake.

247
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:49,890
All signs are pointing to Jung Suk Hee.

248
00:14:50,590 --> 00:14:51,700
I'm sorry, sir.

249
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:54,200
I'll be more thorough this time.

250
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:56,470
There's no time. Go, quickly.

251
00:14:57,940 --> 00:14:59,370
I have a really bad feeling about this.

252
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:03,570
The way that old man looked at me
was full of suspicion.

253
00:15:04,740 --> 00:15:09,050
At this rate, it's only a matter of time
before he finds out I'm not Ma Eun Hye.

254
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:11,250
I can't let that happen.

255
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:14,990
First, I need to go help my Jun Ho
pull himself together.

256
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:31,240
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

257
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:34,870
Jun Ho, it's okay.

258
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:38,710
You have me.
There's no reason to torture yourself.

259
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:41,250
Lee Kang Hyuk is not your father.

260
00:15:41,950 --> 00:15:44,050
You have to trust me, Jun Ho.

261
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:46,920
That's enough.

262
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,820
It's tainted blood either way.

263
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:51,220
What difference does it make whose it is?

264
00:15:52,590 --> 00:15:54,890
I've decided not to dwell on
my parentage anymore.

265
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:57,490
Good.

266
00:16:02,430 --> 00:16:03,630
Baek Ho knows too.

267
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:05,500
That the crest on this golden toad...

268
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:07,970
is Chairman Ma's family crest.

269
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:11,410
To show off his family name,

270
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:13,740
Chairman Ma might have included it
with gifts to powerful people.

271
00:16:14,010 --> 00:16:17,050
He might’ve been flexing his influence.
Don't read too much into it.

272
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:18,450
Anyway, Jun Ho,

273
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:21,120
what's the progress on finding
the largest shareholder, Choi Ha Joon?

274
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:23,920
From what I've gathered, Choi Ha Joon...

275
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,990
has never appeared publicly
in the country.

276
00:16:27,590 --> 00:16:28,890
Not for shareholder meetings,
not for anything.

277
00:16:29,290 --> 00:16:30,930
He has never once shown his face.

278
00:16:32,060 --> 00:16:34,300
It's like he's a ghost.
There's no trace of him anywhere.

279
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,900
Right. Of course.

280
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:39,300
I was just curious to see
how much you'd found out.

281
00:16:40,340 --> 00:16:42,140
If you're going to wear the crown
at Dream Hotel,

282
00:16:42,540 --> 00:16:46,080
you must watch the largest shareholder
and the stock distribution.

283
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:49,050
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

284
00:16:52,180 --> 00:16:55,850
You're acting just like Chae Hwa Young.
Why are you after other people's things?

285
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:58,790
How dare you act this way in front of me,
Lawyer Kang?

286
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:00,960
Then should I report him
to the police for theft?

287
00:17:01,060 --> 00:17:02,530
Lawyer Kang, why don't you let go of him
and talk?

288
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:04,230
Tell me, Kang Jun Ho.

289
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:07,770
Why did you steal it?
What scheme are you pulling?

290
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:10,630
What are you talking about?
I didn't steal it.

291
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:13,940
Yours is the same as the one CEO Chae has,

292
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:17,510
so I brought it here to ask her
if you might be her son.

293
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:19,780
What? Me, CEO Chae's son?

294
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:22,750
- That's ridiculous.
- I know.

295
00:17:23,350 --> 00:17:25,320
I've confirmed that it's ridiculous.

296
00:17:25,850 --> 00:17:27,250
So relax. You're not her son.

297
00:17:28,690 --> 00:17:31,560
But you're going to have to explain
why you have this.

298
00:17:31,620 --> 00:17:33,160
And why would I have to explain
that to you?

299
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:34,490
Are you out of your mind?

300
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:36,490
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

301
00:17:41,130 --> 00:17:45,270
I guess whoever finds out
why Kang Baek Ho has that is the winner.

302
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:49,010
And to do that,
I'll have to sound out Chairman Ma.

303
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:52,210
But there's something fishy
about that old man.

304
00:18:01,250 --> 00:18:04,120
Gosh, my husband looks a little upset.

305
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:07,990
I was upset about something,

306
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,630
but seeing your face
made it all melt away.

307
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,330
You're the one who makes me smile.

308
00:18:16,330 --> 00:18:20,440
- That woman invited your mom to dinner.
- Right.

309
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:22,970
Your mother's treating us today, right?

310
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:25,280
I almost completely forgot.

311
00:18:25,740 --> 00:18:28,150
I'm not sure if my mom remembers.
Let me give her a call.

312
00:18:28,150 --> 00:18:31,320
There's no need.
I spoke with your mother earlier.

313
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:33,150
She said she's coming straight
to Suk Hee's Side Dishes.

314
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:34,790
Of course.

315
00:18:35,390 --> 00:18:37,990
My good wife thinks of everything.

316
00:18:38,890 --> 00:18:39,920
I did good, right?

317
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:44,290
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

318
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:45,530
Oh, my goodness.

319
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:47,200
What did you just say?

320
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:49,830
You mean Chairman Ali...

321
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,870
was actually you?

322
00:18:53,070 --> 00:18:54,070
That's right.

323
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:56,940
My mom fooled the sharp Chae Hwa Young.

324
00:18:57,010 --> 00:18:59,610
My mom's acting deserved
a Best Actress award.

325
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:04,280
Thanks to her, we got 30 million dollars
for the contract penalty fee.

326
00:19:04,350 --> 00:19:06,180
It's because you showed up
at just the right time...

327
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:09,550
and exposed her infidelity.
Everything went smoothly.

328
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:11,490
I'm so very grateful.

329
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,590
That sly vixen, Chae Hwa Young.

330
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:18,700
She must be stewing right now
after losing all that hard-earned money.

331
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:21,000
Compared to her taking my Seo Rin's life,

332
00:19:21,470 --> 00:19:23,930
that 30 million dollars is chump change.

333
00:19:26,670 --> 00:19:27,910
By the way, Baek Ho.

334
00:19:29,010 --> 00:19:33,440
Didn't you say her alibi was perfect
on the day of Seo Rin's death?

335
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,880
And I heard the police
couldn't investigate any further.

336
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:38,480
It's not an alibi.
I bet it's a fabrication.

337
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,420
We're convinced...

338
00:19:40,420 --> 00:19:44,150
she left her phone
at the massage parlor and snuck out.

339
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:45,890
She must have a burner phone...

340
00:19:46,260 --> 00:19:47,860
to contact Manager Lee.

341
00:19:47,860 --> 00:19:51,930
And we have to prove that Chae Hwa Young
went to that hospital...

342
00:19:51,930 --> 00:19:53,130
with Seo Rin.

343
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:56,070
That's the only way we can make
Chae Hwa Young pay for her crimes,

344
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:58,400
but we're hitting a wall,
and it's so frustrating.

345
00:19:58,570 --> 00:19:59,800
Twelve times a day...

346
00:20:00,770 --> 00:20:01,910
No, thousands of times...

347
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:05,510
I kill Chae Hwa Young in my heart...

348
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:07,410
who killed Bok Gil and Seo Rin,

349
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:10,910
I swear I'll catch Chae Hwa Young
with my own two hands...

350
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:13,720
and make her pay for her crimes.

351
00:20:14,890 --> 00:20:15,890
Ms. Jung...

352
00:20:16,850 --> 00:20:17,850
Oh, dear.

353
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:22,690
I'm so sorry. I got carried away.
Especially with my honored guest here,

354
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:25,630
I shouldn't have said such awful things
at the dinner table.

355
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:27,130
Please, eat up.

356
00:20:28,870 --> 00:20:30,700
Is the food to your liking?

357
00:20:30,930 --> 00:20:34,500
Of course. This is a magnificent feast.

358
00:20:35,770 --> 00:20:38,640
I've never had such delicious food before.

359
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:42,450
Right, Mom? Now you see
why I eat here all the time.

360
00:20:43,150 --> 00:20:46,020
- I do.
- Eat up, Baek Ho.

361
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:47,080
I will.

362
00:20:48,650 --> 00:20:49,750
It really is delicious.

363
00:20:50,850 --> 00:20:52,360
- Here, try this.
- Please eat.

364
00:20:54,020 --> 00:20:55,460
Seeing my Baek Ho...

365
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:58,730
so loved by his mother-in-law...

366
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:02,370
makes me so happy
and puts my heart at ease.

367
00:21:04,770 --> 00:21:05,770
Go on, eat.

368
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:08,440
- Okay, I'm eating.
- You eat too, Jang Mi.

369
00:21:17,050 --> 00:21:18,180
Kang Hyuk.

370
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:20,720
Young Ja. What brings you here?

371
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:23,290
I just had tea with Baek Ho
and was about to leave.

372
00:21:24,250 --> 00:21:26,490
- Please, get in.
- Thank you.

373
00:21:29,790 --> 00:21:30,790
Doors closing.

374
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:33,300
- What floor?
- First floor.

375
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:36,670
I see you didn't drive today.

376
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:39,840
Yes, driving's gotten
a little tiring lately.

377
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:43,240
I get tired so easily.
I'm just going to grab a cab.

378
00:21:44,140 --> 00:21:46,280
And where are you headed?

379
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:48,050
I've got something to take care of
in Yeongdeungpo.

380
00:21:48,250 --> 00:21:51,680
What a coincidence.
I'm heading that way myself.

381
00:21:51,820 --> 00:21:53,620
Why don't you come with me then?

382
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:55,590
That works out perfectly.

383
00:21:56,320 --> 00:21:58,520
Then I'll get us coffee on the way.

384
00:22:09,670 --> 00:22:10,670
Here.

385
00:22:11,470 --> 00:22:14,070
- What's this?
- I grabbed one from the office earlier,

386
00:22:14,470 --> 00:22:16,010
I must've known I was going to see you.

387
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:19,110
But this is yours, isn't it?

388
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,740
I already had one.

389
00:22:25,380 --> 00:22:26,380
What's wrong?

390
00:22:27,850 --> 00:22:29,590
I left my phone behind.

391
00:22:30,320 --> 00:22:32,190
Just wait here for a minute.
Enjoy the coffee.

392
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:34,790
- I'll be right back.
- Okay, hurry back.

393
00:22:45,300 --> 00:22:46,300
Baek Ho.

394
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:49,470
I want to help take revenge
on Chae Hwa Young.

395
00:22:50,370 --> 00:22:52,710
To prove she caused Seo Rin's death,

396
00:22:52,980 --> 00:22:54,510
what did you say was the first step?

397
00:22:54,910 --> 00:22:56,310
If we can get proof
that CEO Chae or Manager Lee...

398
00:22:56,380 --> 00:23:00,120
went with Seo Rin
to that plastic surgery clinic,

399
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:01,320
it'll make things a lot easier.

400
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:04,890
Okay, I got it. I'll look into it, too.

401
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:14,600
Oh my, what a mess.

402
00:23:17,530 --> 00:23:20,940
Kang Hyuk seemed like such a neat freak.

403
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,370
He has a messy side.

404
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,840
(Parking Receipt, Medical Public Parking
License Plate: 237BU8305)

405
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:26,810
He was parked for six whole hours.

406
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,580
"Medical" in Ohjeong?

407
00:23:31,350 --> 00:23:32,520
"May 11?"

408
00:23:33,580 --> 00:23:35,150
That's the day Director Ma died.

409
00:23:35,690 --> 00:23:37,350
Oh my goodness. This is it.

410
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:54,440
Hey, what's wrong? Are you out of breath?

411
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,270
No, I'm fine.

412
00:23:58,340 --> 00:24:01,040
I just have a habit of sighing sometimes.

413
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:04,580
Oh, dear. What should I do?

414
00:24:04,850 --> 00:24:08,220
Baek Ho wanted me to join him
and Director Ma,

415
00:24:08,290 --> 00:24:10,350
and it completely slipped my mind.

416
00:24:10,650 --> 00:24:13,490
Baek Ho just called
and told me to hurry over,

417
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:17,590
- and I've just been watching your car.
- Is that so?

418
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:21,570
But didn't you say
you had to go to Yeongdeungpo?

419
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:27,300
It was just a class reunion.
It's not a big deal if I miss it.

420
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:30,310
Gosh, what a shame.

421
00:24:30,370 --> 00:24:34,610
I was so looking forward to our drive,
even if it was short.

422
00:24:34,810 --> 00:24:35,980
Such a shame.

423
00:24:36,780 --> 00:24:38,920
Don't worry about it.
There's always next time.

424
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:43,090
This was so thoughtful of you.

425
00:24:43,150 --> 00:24:45,320
I'll treat you to something delicious
next time.

426
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,090
Drive safe.

427
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:48,360
I will.

428
00:25:05,740 --> 00:25:07,610
(Parking Receipt, Medical Public Parking
License Plate: 237BU8305)

429
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:13,880
Look at this.

430
00:25:14,550 --> 00:25:16,120
This is Chae Hwa Young's license plate,
right?

431
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:21,460
I took some photos while investigating
Kang Nam Bong and Chae Hwa Young's affair,

432
00:25:21,760 --> 00:25:23,690
and the plate number matches.

433
00:25:23,690 --> 00:25:25,960
That's right. It's her license plate.

434
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:30,770
So they lied about the massage parlor.
They were at Ohjeong Plastic Surgery.

435
00:25:30,870 --> 00:25:32,340
And all that time, my Seo Rin was...

436
00:25:33,670 --> 00:25:36,440
To think they would go so far
as to lie about it.

437
00:25:37,570 --> 00:25:40,110
Mom, thank you so much.

438
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:44,680
I never imagined I'd find
Chae Hwa Young's parking receipt in there.

439
00:25:44,810 --> 00:25:48,250
I was actually planning to snoop
through Lee Kang Hyuk's phone.

440
00:25:48,990 --> 00:25:49,990
Thanks, Mom.

441
00:25:53,660 --> 00:25:58,300
(Log in)

442
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,900
(12-5 Sogong-dong, Choi Myung Chul)

443
00:26:07,140 --> 00:26:08,710
(12-5 Sogong-dong, Choi Myung Chul)

444
00:26:08,770 --> 00:26:10,140
(1994-1995 VIP Appreciation Gift Ledger)

445
00:26:16,850 --> 00:26:18,210
(November 30, 1994,
Choi Myung Chul, 12-5 Sogong-dong)

446
00:26:18,280 --> 00:26:19,850
(375 grams of solid gold toad
engraved with the family crest)

447
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:22,050
(Commemorating the Sogong-dong Hotel deal,
Delivered by Chairman Ma Dae Chang)

448
00:26:22,150 --> 00:26:23,450
"Commemorating the deal?"

449
00:26:23,450 --> 00:26:24,650
A deal was finalized?

450
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:29,260
A week later, the fire broke out.
And my grandfather passed away.

451
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:32,100
So, was it just an accidental fire?

452
00:26:32,730 --> 00:26:36,370
If it was an accident,
then why was I sent to the infant home?

453
00:26:49,050 --> 00:26:52,080
Lawyer Kang, what brings you here?

454
00:26:52,180 --> 00:26:55,250
There's something
I wanted to ask you in private, sir.

455
00:26:55,390 --> 00:26:56,890
Really?

456
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:02,330
I was wondering what this is.

457
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,610
Wait...

458
00:27:16,370 --> 00:27:17,510
This is...

459
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:22,550
So that's why you asked me...

460
00:27:22,650 --> 00:27:23,850
about the golden toad.

461
00:27:24,050 --> 00:27:25,050
Yes.

462
00:27:25,050 --> 00:27:28,350
I was under the impression
this is your family's crest.

463
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:32,720
I also heard you only give
this precious gift to family members.

464
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:36,260
- Is that true?
- Yes, that's right.

465
00:27:37,060 --> 00:27:41,000
So then, why do you have this?

466
00:27:41,630 --> 00:27:43,830
That's exactly what
I came here to find out.

467
00:27:44,430 --> 00:27:48,640
I'd like to know
why I have this golden toad...

468
00:27:48,870 --> 00:27:50,210
with your family's crest on it.

469
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,840
(The First Man)

470
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:26,510
Choi Myung Chul.

471
00:28:26,710 --> 00:28:30,310
So, in the end,
you've sent your grandson to me.

472
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:32,350
He said he and my grandfather
were best friends?

473
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:34,180
Then why do I have
such a bad feeling about this?

474
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:38,020
- Is Baek Ho really Choi Ha Joon?
- Have you found out who Choi Ha Joon is?

475
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,990
Where can I find Choi Ha Joon, then?

476
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:42,860
It turns out that so-called Chairman Ali
is an impostor.

477
00:28:43,130 --> 00:28:45,400
Is this Jung Suk Hee?

478
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,560
Has she regained her senses?

479
00:28:48,900 --> 00:28:50,900
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
